|  18 |  11 | DC1  |   |  50 |  31 | 1    |   |  82 |  51 | Q    |   | 114 |  71 | q    |
|  19 |  12 | DC2  |   |  51 |  32 | 2    |   |  83 |  52 | R    |   | 115 |  72 | r    |
|  20 |  13 | DC3  |   |  52 |  33 | 3    |   |  84 |  53 | S    |   | 116 |  73 | s    |
|  21 |  14 | DC4  |   |  53 |  34 | 4    |   |  85 |  54 | T    |   | 117 |  74 | t    |
|  22 |  15 | NAK  |   |  54 |  35 | 5    |   |  86 |  55 | U    |   | 118 |  75 | u    |
|  23 |  16 | SYN  |   |  55 |  36 | 6    |   |  87 |  56 | V    |   | 119 |  76 | v    |
|  24 |  17 | ETB  |   |  56 |  37 | 7    |   |  88 |  57 | W    |   | 120 |  77 | w    |
|  25 |  18 | CAN  |   |  57 |  38 | 8    |   |  89 |  58 | X    |   | 121 |  78 | x    |
|  26 |  19 | EM   |   |  58 |  39 | 9    |   |  90 |  59 | Y    |   | 122 |  79 | y    |
|  27 |  1A | SUB  |   |  59 |  3A | :    |   |  91 |  5A | Z    |   | 123 |  7A | z    |
|  28 |  1B | ESC  |   |  60 |  3B | ;    |   |  92 |  5B | [    |   | 124 |  7B | {    |
|  29 |  1C | FS   |   |  61 |  3C | <    |   |  93 |  5C | \    |   | 125 |  7C |      |
|  30 |  1D | GS   |   |  62 |  3D | =    |   |  94 |  5D | ]    |   | 126 |  7D | }    |
